---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';
import { webPageSchema, breadcrumbSchema } from '../utils/schema';

const schema = [
  webPageSchema('Cancellation and Refund Policy', 'eLan Technology cancellation and refund policy for web design and digital services.', '/cancellation-refund-policy'),
  breadcrumbSchema([{ name: 'Home', url: '/' }, { name: 'Cancellation and Refund Policy', url: '/cancellation-refund-policy' }]),
];
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Cancellation and Refund Policy"
  description="eLan Technology cancellation and refund policy for web design and digital services."
  lastUpdated="2025-01-01"
>
  <SchemaMarkup schema={schema} />

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    eLan Technology aims for complete client satisfaction on every project. This policy outlines the
    conditions under which cancellations are accepted and refunds may be issued for each of our
    service categories. We encourage clients to contact us to discuss any concerns before initiating
    a cancellation.
  </p>

  <h2>Web Design &amp; Development Projects</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      The 50% advance payment is <strong>non-refundable</strong> once design or development work has
      commenced, as it covers the time and resources allocated to your project.
    </li>
    <li>
      If eLan Technology fails to deliver the agreed project scope within the agreed timeline through
      no fault of the client, a pro-rata refund of the advance may be considered and issued at our
      discretion.
    </li>
    <li>
      No refund will be issued after final delivery and the client has provided written sign-off or
      approval.
    </li>
    <li>
      If a project is cancelled by the client <em>before commencement</em> (i.e., before any design
      or development work has begun), a full refund of the advance will be issued minus a 10%
      administrative processing charge.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Digital Marketing &amp; SEO Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Monthly retainer fees are <strong>non-refundable</strong> once work for that month has
      commenced (including strategy, content creation, campaign setup, or reporting).
    </li>
    <li>
      Cancellation of a digital marketing retainer requires <strong>30 days written notice</strong>
      prior to the next billing cycle.
    </li>
    <li>
      Advertising spend (Google Ads, Meta Ads, or other paid social media platforms) is passed
      directly to those platforms and is <strong>non-refundable</strong> under any circumstances.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Maintenance Plans</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Monthly plans:</strong> may be cancelled at any time with 30 days written notice. No
      partial-month refunds are issued.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Annual plans:</strong> a pro-rata refund for unused complete months will be issued if
      the plan is cancelled after the first 3 months of service. No refund is available for
      cancellations within the first 3 months.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Products (Portals &amp; Custom Software)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      The 50% advance payment for custom product or software development is
      <strong>non-refundable</strong> once development work has commenced.
    </li>
    <li>
      All custom software deliverables include a <strong>90-day bug-fix warranty</strong> period. This
      warranty covers defects in the delivered software and does not constitute grounds for a refund.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Refund Process</h2>
  <p>
    Where a refund is approved under this policy, it will be processed within
    <strong>7 to 14 business days</strong> via the original payment method used at the time of
    purchase. Refunds cannot be issued to a different account or payment method.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    To initiate a cancellation or enquire about a refund, please contact our billing team:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:billing@elan-tech.net">billing@elan-tech.net</a></li>
    <li>WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/918788834630">+91 8788834630</a></li>
    <li>
      Address: eLan Technology, Basement Floor, PTG IT Park, Plot No. 21, IT Park Rd,
      Gayatri Nagar, Nagpur, Maharashtra 440022, India
    </li>
  </ul>
</LegalLayout>
